# Absolute URL of a LaTeX render backend that accepts `POST { latex }`.
# Leave unset for a static deploy — the Live-render preview is hidden and the
# app runs as a pure client-side converter.
#
# In `npm run dev` the backend is served automatically at /api/render, so you
# do NOT need to set this for local development.
#
# VITE_RENDER_API=https://your-render-backend.example.com/api/render
